Empowered women, empower women! ğŸ’ªâ€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
As a woman founded and run brand, we believe in this wholeheartedly. ğŸ§¡â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
A letter from our founder, @amyliu47 ğŸ‘‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
Starting a new business is hard and I had a head start after 15 years in the beauty industry. I am grateful to have the privilege of education, experience, and network which made all of it easier. And trust me, itâ€™s still hard.â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
Two years ago, I got an email asking if Tower 28 would be offering grants or loans for Black-owned small businesses as some other beauty brands have pledged. As a small company ourselves, I wrote her back and told her that we are unable to offer financial help but that I would be happy to set up time to give her advice if that would help. And that got me thinking â€”maybe I canâ€™t offer money, but I could offer my time, resources, knowledge, and lessons learned from the front lines... and what if I could get a few girl bosses from the industry to do the same?â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
And thatâ€™s how Clean Beauty Summer School was born. â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
Together, we are a group of Founders and beauty industry experts who understand firsthand the struggle and challenges of starting a brand because we are IN IT. Our mission is simple, to come together and collectively share our most valuable resource - time, mentorship, network and education - in an effort to accelerate BIPOC-owned Beauty businesses and make the Beauty industry better, more diverse, and inclusive.â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
â €â €â €â €â €â €â €â €â €â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
Tower 28â€™s mission from the beginning has been to make clean beauty more accessible for EVERYONE. We are thrilled to help bring our mission to the beauty industry and make change from the inside out.â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
We're so excited to bring back CBSS for the third year in a row, and applications open very very soon!! â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹â€‹
